{"tid":416413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青衣都起插針公屋？！","createTime":"2017-09-27T18:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T07:50:22.000Z","uid":3659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f0225cc3cc506148254014eb0004f66c96f17100","tid":416413,"uid":3659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T18:01:06.000Z","msg":"有冇長青撚依到？<br />\n<br />\n長青邨擬建4座40層高插針式公屋大廈<br />\n<br />\n地盤範圍包括現有長青巴士總站、長青社區中心、前張熾昌小學、青松樓對出停車場及球場、青桃樓旁籃球場。<br />\n<br />\n房屋署建議於上址興建4幢約40層高公營住宅樓宇，約提供3,050個單位，新增人口約8,550人，預計於2018年起分三期動工，料於2028年全數落成。<br />\n<br />\n區議會房屋事務委員會將於10月3日的會議上討論上述計劃。（source:蘋果日報，葵青區議會）<br />\n--------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">賣個廣告，各位葵青巴絲未入嘅快d入啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地好欠缺人手，尤其係core<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有興趣嘅可以telegram聯絡我地<br />\n<br />\n請即加入Telegram group:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ktrhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fktrhk&d=6clDZj5U5g6bBJ2Gyn2rAZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=871f3025\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ktrhk</a></span><br />\n--------------------------------------------<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/015906_f18368a4c53e5e07d2a8c7d202846929.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F015906_f18368a4c53e5e07d2a8c7d202846929.jpg&h=70ffcae8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78a9f9d6db99ec5f8ec484162f8f0dafe0e8def0","tid":416413,"uid":3659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T18:01:56.000Z","msg":"深夜一推"},{"pid":"c58cf035d4aa9f2af9704b7a3e20d46b9b653a1d","tid":416413,"uid":43941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T18:03:25.000Z","msg":"係咪葵青區唯一有蓋室外籃球場(好似係)個到？"},{"pid":"1224d27e6a80516cb869f58f8055fe84fa5736ba","tid":416413,"uid"